high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the sink at the other end.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Turn right and walk towards the fridge.
Place the cup on the top shelf inside the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on the counter to your right.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the right and find the sink.
Pick up the mug from inside the sink.
Turn right to go around the island and locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the mug inside. Shut the fridge door. Then open the door and get the mug out and shut the door.
Take the mug and go left around the island to the coffee maker.
Place the mug under the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Chill a mug for some coffee.

high_descs: turn around and walk to the end of the room, then turn right and walk to the other end of the room, then another right until you have reached the sink on the left, turn left to face the sink
grab the cup out of the left side of the sink
turn right and walk to the end of the room, then hang a right and walk until you've reached the fridge on your left, then turn to face the fridge on your left
place the cup inside of the fridge to cool, close the door, then open the door and take the cup back out after it has cooled
turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk until you reach the coffee maker on the kitchen counter to your right, turn right to face the coffee maker once you're there
place the cup under the pouring spout of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a cooled cup under the coffee maker spout
